#BlackMagicCraft #Episode172 #3dPrinting

In this video I set up my Anycubic Photon resin printer. I get help from my friend Danny (@3D Printed Tabletop) levelling it and helping me do my first test print. 

@3D Printed Tabletop:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCr_uz-iWzyR1VJNlN-E1y7w

LOST ADVENTURES KICKSTARTER: http://kck.st/2KgEWSS

Anycubic did send me this printer for free but I was not otherwise paid, or obligated to, make this video. As I mentioned there are a few good options for resin printers and this is not necessarily the one I would have purchased myself.
